data.description: This beautiful ranch home is handicap-accessible.  Since purchasing it in 2020, the owners have sealed the roof with a Roofmax warranty; put in all new Thermopane windows; a new and wider back door; new Shaw brand LVP flooring in the kitchen; new kitchen appliances; painted the interior; remodeled both main floor bathrooms; new furnace, central air, tankless water heater, and water softener and chlorine remover.  The garage has a new auto door opener.  There are steps as well as a ramp to enter the home.  There is also a ramp for the front porch if wanted. A chairlift provides access to the basement.  This 1+ acre lot has multiple grape arbors, and fruit~cherry, peach, apple, apricot~trees out back as well as weeping cherry and peach trees in the front.  Includes rhubarb and gardens and American chestnut trees.  All this and you are close to the Allegheny River with its amenities.  THIS IS A MUST SEE!!
